lse Midt-Norge, Trond Michael Andersen, som selv har jobbet i oljebransjen i tillegg til h\u00f8yskolemilj\u00f8et, er enig med H\u00f8ie.", "\u2013 Vi skal gj\u00f8re hva vi kan. Det skal st\u00e5 \u00f8verst p\u00e5 listen i ethvert lederm\u00f8te vi har fremover, s\u00e5 gir det forh\u00e5pentligvis resultater, sier han."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|nordtrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "1b8a24129d0a2b3e9e1f688f926713448f67abc3821238d00559dcf5fe34351b"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-01T17:02:21.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Oljebarn og helseminister Bent H\u00f8ie (H) trekker frem Statoil som et eksempel til etterf\u00f8lgelse."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/nordtrondelag/article8654109.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/JPS_helseminister25.JPG"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/4ec8703e93fa623a39128e82b24b1796ba6f4588.jpg?59676519"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "\u2013 Helse-Norge m\u00e5 l\u00e6re av oljebransjen -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "4ec8703e93fa623a39128e82b24b1796ba6f4588"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "nordtrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "statoil"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["helse", "l\u00e6re", "oljebransjen", "jobb"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["helse midt-norge", "tangen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "stj\u00f8rdal"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person